  "title": "练习成效高度依赖于方法设计",
  "content": "<p data-pid=\"LXohrmk1\">朴素的练习方法收效甚微：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zALB77pBFKPZae7f5kD3ro1\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">采用朴素方法的练习会让人迅速遭遇瓶颈期</a><sup data-text=\"采用朴素方法的练习会让人迅速遭遇瓶颈期\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1929184582483285376\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup>。但这并非简单地用一种更优的方法取代原有方法就行，因为<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zS1N4F9fUeMQ1kYHVAvwVAU\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">突破瓶颈期往往需要另辟蹊径</a><sup data-text=\"突破瓶颈期往往需要另辟蹊径\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1929184438018875845\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"2\">[2]</sup>。练习方法必须随着个人水平的提升而不断演进，因为<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zV6BU6otjQF7BPeJkskyoaT\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">发展技能需要挑战稳态</a><sup data-text=\"发展技能需要挑战稳态\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/422370272\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"3\">[3]</sup>。</p><p data-pid=\"9reGlRin\">这往往意味着练习方法必须由专家来设计与维护：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z852Vpw9YE5hD3mGs6ScCWJ\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">专业教练会促进有效的刻意练习</a><sup data-text=\"专业教练会促进有效的刻意练习\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1929184112222118603\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"4\">[4]</sup>。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><hr/><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><h2><b>参考文献</b></h2><p data-pid=\"-eYqoVPJ\">Ericsson, K. A., Krampe, R. T., &amp; Tesch-Römer, C. (1993). The role of deliberate practice in the acquisition of expert performance.<i>Psychological Review</i>,<i>100</i>(3), 363.<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/Ericsson_et_al_-_The_Role_of_Deliberate_Practice_in_the_Acquisition_of_Expert_Performance\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Ericsson et al - The Role of Deliberate Practice in the Acquisition of Expert Performance</a></p><blockquote data-pid=\"0ZZ8rpn2\">一个正确的方法或策略所具有的至关重要性，也已在日期计算、心算乘法、对颜色和音高的绝对判断、运动技能以及工作方法等领域得到证实。</blockquote><p data-pid=\"LgV8PVAb\">（第367页）</p><h2>链接至本文（已汉化）</h2><ul><li data-pid=\"ycWluiRq\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1929184112222118603\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">专业教练会促进有效的刻意练习</a></li><li data-pid=\"n3HmwZYQ\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1929184438018875845\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">突破瓶颈期往往需要另辟蹊径</a></li></ul><h2>声明</h2><p data-pid=\"dOLMWPGm\">此内容发布由 Andy Matuschak 许可。未经允许，不得转载或修改。保留所有权利。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><blockquote data-pid=\"g67dMnJu\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制 <br/>感谢主要译者 gemini-2.5-pro，校对 Jarrett Ye<br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zXDPKHgmQSdevyW1N2iiaSy\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Practice efficacy is highly sensitive to method design</a></blockquote>",
